<h2>Dashboard: Admin Panel <i>IIIT KOTA</i></h2>
<p>Role: </p>
<p>Ip: {{this.ip}}</p>
<br /><br />
<h3>Generate cloud link:</h3>
<p>If your action requires images first generate their urls here.</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-4 col-lg-3 crd">
    Generate cloud stored link
    <form id="upload-form" action="/upload?token={{this.token}}" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
      <h3>Select an image to upload:</h3>
      <div class="upload-container"><input id="file-picker" type="file" name="image"></div>
      <div><input class="btn btn-warning" type="submit" value="Upload Image"></div>
    </form>
  </div>
  {{!-- <div class="col-lg-2">
  </div> --}}
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-6">
    <div
      style="height:240px;width:100%;border:1px solid #F4A460;overflow:auto;">

      <ol class="list-group">
        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-warning">Links generated so far....</li>
        {{#each this.resources1}}
        <li class="list-group-item">https://{{../accountName}}.blob.core.windows.net/{{../containerName}}/{{name}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br />
<h3>Add new or Remove existing faculties here</h3>
<p>Please note that, your activites will be recorded</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3 crd">
    <h4>Add New Faculty👨‍🏫</h4>
    <h3>Click the button to proceed</h3>
    <p>This feature is only for admins, not coadmins</p>
    <a href="/add/faculty?token={{this.token}}" style="text-decoration: none;"><button id="addfaculty"
        class="btn btn-lg btn-warning">Add</button></a>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6  col-lg-3 crd">
    <h4>Remove Faculty👩‍🏫</h4>
    <h3>Click the button to proceed</h3>
    <p>This feature is only for admins, not coadmins</p>
    <a href="/remove/faculty?token={{this.token}}" style="text-decoration: none;"><button id="removefaculty"
        class="btn btn-lg btn-warning">Remove</button></a>

  </div>
</div>
<br /><br />
<h3>Create Notice/News/Article here..</h3>
<p>Please note that, your activites will be recorded</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-4 col-lg-3 crd">
    <h3>Add New Notice📑</h3>
    <p>Rememeber once you have created one, you <strong>cannot</strong> delete it.</p>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#staticBackdrop">Add</button>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-4 col-lg-3 crd">
    <h4>Add News 📰</h4>
    <p>Rememeber once added you <strong>cannot</strong> delete it.</p>
    <h5>News is an simplified combination of notice and article</h5>
    <button id="addnews" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning"data-toggle="modal" data-target="#staticBackdrop2">Add</button>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-4 col-lg-3 crd">
    <h4>Add New Article 📕</h4>
    <p>Rememeber once added you <strong>cannot</strong> delete it.</p>
    <h5>More powerful comming soon!</h5>
    <a href="/add/article?token={{this.token}}"><button id="addarticle" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning">Add</button>
  </a></div>
</div>
<div class="modal fade" id="staticBackdrop" data-backdrop="static" tabindex="-1" role="dialog"
  aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="staticBackdropLabel">Create New Notice</h5>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Note: Once created you cannot delete it. <br />Also, your ip will be recorded for security purposes.</p>
        <form action="/add/notice?token={{this.token}}" method="post">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="title">Title</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="title" aria-describedby="title" name="title">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="description">Brief Description</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="description" name="description" rows="3"></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="validity">Expiration Date</label>
            <input type="date" class="form-control" id="validity" min="2020-03-31" name="validity">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning btn-sm">Submit</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="modal fade bd-example-modal-lg" id="staticBackdrop2" data-backdrop="static" tabindex="-1" role="dialog"
  aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="staticBackdropLabel">Add News</h5>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Note: Once created you cannot delete it. <br />Also, your ip will be recorded for security purposes.</p>
        <form action="/add/news?token={{this.token}}" method="post">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="title">Title</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="title" aria-describedby="title" name="title">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="description">Description</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="description" name="description" rows="7"></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="photourl">Head Image URL</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="photourl"name="photourl">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning btn-sm">Submit</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
<br /><br />
